public class JDevAuditRunner
extends oracle.jdeveloper.test.JDevRunner

The JUnit runner for running JUnit tests for JAudit. This runner extends the ST provided JDevRunner. It does two things. First, it sets a magic system property called BUILT that indicates to the runner where to find JDeveloper install. Second, it makes sure the psrjunit.jar will get deleted. This jar contains JUnit classes which cause a class conflict during runtime.
